  "comment": "ADJ Encore FR150z: Part of the Encore stage lighting series, the Encore FR150Z lighting fixture is equipped with an 8-inch Fresnel lens and powered by a 130W LED engine. It produces a white wide, soft-edged beam for stage and theatre use at 3000K. It comes with barn doors to adjust the beam dispersion and a manual know to change the beam angle from 15 to 38 degrees.\nThe Encore FR150Z has a 4-button LCD operational menu, 3-pin and 5-pin DMX In/Out and Locking Power In/Out to daisy chain the power from one fixture to another. ",
